		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/pink/"  >P!nk</a>周一（10 月 16 日）宣布，由于“家庭健康问题”，她推迟了刚刚推出的 Trustfall 巡演中的两场演出。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>受影响的两场演出是周二和周三在华盛顿州塔科马举行的音乐会。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pink-Performs-At-Chase-Field-oct-2023-billboard-pro-1260.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="P!nk" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> P!nk 暂停耗资 2.5 亿美元的夏季嘉年华，开始 Trustfall 巡演</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2023年10月16日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> P!nk 在分享给 Instagram 的消息中写道：“我很遗憾地通知塔科马门票持有者，10 月 17 日和 10 月 18 日（明天和周三）的两场演出将被推迟。” “Live Nation 正在努力重新安排未来的日期。家庭医疗问题需要我们立即关注。对于由此造成的任何不便，我向大家致以最诚挚的歉意。我只向所有人传递爱和健康。”</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> P!nk 的 Trustfall 巡演已进行了三场演出，该巡演于周四在加利福尼亚州萨克拉门托启动，周末在旧金山举行了两场演出。这位流行歌手刚刚结束了夏季嘉年华体育场巡演的北美站，巡演的日期还剩 11 月 26 日在德克萨斯州阿灵顿举行，此前她因鼻窦感染取消了 9 月份的演出，并将在 2019 年恢复演出。澳大利亚和新西兰二月。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>据<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/pink-summer-carnival-earnings-before-trustfall-tour/"  >Billboard Boxscore 报道的</a>数据显示，夏季嘉年华迄今为止已收获 2.576 亿美元的收入，并在 41 场演出中售出 180 万张门票。夏季嘉年华首先在欧洲举办了 19 场演出，售出 871,000 张门票，收入 1.068 亿美元，随后抵达美国和加拿大，售出 914,000 张门票，收入 1.507 亿美元。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>她目前的巡演是为了支持她的第九张录音室专辑<em>《Trustfall》</em> ，该专辑于 2 月 17 日通过 RCA 发行。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>请参阅下面 P!nk 的 Instagram 消息： </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-instagram wp-block-embed-instagram"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CyeepuYvSAX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:500px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4;border-radius: 50%;flex-grow: 0;height: 40px;margin-right: 14px;width: 40px"></div><div style="flex-direction: column;flex-grow: 1;justify-content: center"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4;border-radius: 4px;flex-grow: 0;height: 14px;margin-bottom: 6px;width: 100px"></div><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4;border-radius: 4px;flex-grow: 0;height: 14px;width: 60px"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0"></div><div style="height:50px;margin:0 auto 12px;width:50px"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g fill="none"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058,72.155 56